'''Joe Brozowski''' is a comic book penciller who drew an issue of the [[Star Wars (1977)|''Marvel Star Wars'']] series. He also was the regular illustrator for the [[Wikipedia:DC Comics|DC Comics]] title [[Wikipedia:Firestorm (comics)|''The Fury of Firestorm'']] in the late 1980s.

